# MinervaSâ€‘ODH Connector

Skeleton project that bridges **MinervaS** (fleet guidance) with **OpenDataHub** weather & traffic APIs
for the *A22 Trentino* road segment.

> Generated on 2025-05-05

## Quick start

```bash
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate  # Windows: .venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -e '.[docs,test]'
pytest            # run sample tests
cd docs && make html   # build HTML docs (needs Sphinx)
```

